isoft-os-prober

System Bus service for os-prober.


Build && Install

$ mkdir build
$ cd build
$ cmake .. -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr
$ make -j4
# make install
# systemctl enable isoft-os-prober-daemon


Debug

$ cmake .. -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr  \
    -DENABLE_DEBUG=ON
$ make
# ./daemon/isoft-os-prober-daemon

